ver/xml stack transitively, and meaningful coverage is reachable with an embedded Jetty WebAppContext plus temporary webapp files.\",\n  \"deterministic_setup\": [],\n  \"agent_guidance\": \"No required environment variables or system properties. Tests can use a temporary exploded webapp directory with WEB-INF/web.xml and run an embedded Server/WebAppContext on loopback. If exercising WebAppClassLoader.Context directly, account for the 9.4.0.RC1 API change by implementing the Class<?>-based isSystemClass/isServerClass methods and the isServerResource/isSystemResource methods.\",\n  \"risks\": [\n    \"The current compile failure appears to be an API drift in WebAppClassLoader.Context between tested Jetty versions, not a missing dependency or external service.\",\n    \"Optional Jetty modules such as jetty-jmx, annotation scanning, JSP, or external servlet containers are not needed for core jetty-webapp descriptor/classloader/WebAppContext coverage and should not be added unless tests intentionally cover those optional features.\"\n  ]\n}", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0e8c5874c9951e02016a41f9cd5af08195baaa64a16d497e5d\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 4794, "output": 775, "cacheRead": 19456, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 25025, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1782708675168, "responseId": "resp_0e8c5874c9951e02016a41f9c3c2f881959faa21227edd13c3"}, "toolResults": []}
